# Security

## Supported Versions

| Version | Supported          |
| ------- | ------------------ |
| 0.9.x   | :white_check_mark: |
| < 0.9   | :x:                |

## Reporting a Vulnerability

To report a vulnerability, please open a private vulnerability report at
https://github.com/JasonWeinzierl/eslint-plugin-rxjs-x/security .
